| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1100 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4b03b7cb-c937-50c7-8650-86a8f065c3cf"
